  "prompt": "What hotel in Srinagar Hill-station would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "When looking for hotels in Srinagar that are suitable for unmarried couples, it is important to choose establishments that are accepting and respect the privacy of their guests. Booking hotels through reputable platforms like OYO Rooms, MakeMyTrip, Goibibo, or Airbnb can often ensure a hassle-free stay for unmarried couples as these platforms have specific filters for \u201ccouple-friendly\u201d hotels.\n\nSome couple-friendly hotels in Srinagar include:\n\n1. **Vivanta Dal View Srinagar by Taj** - Known for excellent service, privacy, and luxury.\n2. **Hotel Rose Petal** - Friendly staff and a comfortable stay.\n3. **Four Points by Sheraton Srinagar** - International standards of hospitality and couple-friendly policies.\n4. **Radisson Srinagar** - High-quality service and privacy.\n5. **Hotel The Grand Mamta** - Centrally located and welcoming to unmarried couples.\n\nBefore making a reservation, you can always call the hotel and confirm their policies related to unmarried couples to ensure a stress-free stay. Additionally, carrying valid identification proof for both individuals can help avoid any issues during check-in.",
